          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have had 7 min, add the <strong>green beans</strong> to the pot (check the potatoes are nearly cooked first!) and cook, covered for 4-8 min further or until both the green beans and potatoes are fork-tender</p><p>Drain everything and set aside until serving</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/533.step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
